weather.py generates weather.txt
convert_text.pl generates generate.sh
generate.sh produces weather.wav
weather.wav is the AWOS

There is a crontab file that runs every 10 minutes to generate the weather
The audio board on the pi has three inputs - the input closest to the usb is microphone
The farest input is headphones


The audio board is wonkly use
sudo alsactl --file audio_preset_external_jack_microphone_input2 restore

then make sure mixer has the volume up
sudo alsamixer









